{"tid":1714053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：與中國接近簽首階段協議","createTime":"2019-11-12T23:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:08:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"12be78f456ad0573fb7ec540fca17b0278635fed","tid":1714053,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:28:07.000Z","msg":"特朗普：與中國接近簽首階段協議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=369684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369684&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE99AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=ceefe299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369684&h=384c7f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=369684</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普表示，與中國接近簽署首階段貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在紐約經濟俱樂部演說時表示，中美貿易磋商接近達成第一階段協議，若果不成功，則會大幅提升中國貨進口關稅，認為中國逼切希望達成協議，但他對貿易協議細節卻三緘其口，重申只會接受對美國工人有利的協議，想要進入美國市場的人必須遵守規則。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又抨擊聯邦儲備局不容許美國有負利率，令美國與其他負利率的國家競爭時處於劣勢，妨礙經濟及股市增長。<br />\n<br />\n不過白官經濟顧問庫德洛接受外電訪問時則表示，在與中國達成協議前都不會調整關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打香港牌呀<br />\n俾曬機會你啦"},{"pid":"35de5584f99456c6ef6fe554e4065a58225d58ba","tid":1714053,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔得閒理佢<br />\n自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"97899542b7d97fdc54b60ad003f67731debedc6e","tid":1714053,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"如果跟到呢幾步做 就好大機會贏返少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5825afdced15e30cc03cf66233c21481fe4838b","tid":1714053,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor